# MEMORY.md — Your AI assistant's long-term memory
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file is loaded into every Claude response as context.
# Edit it to give your assistant background knowledge about you.
# MEMORY.md is in .gitignore — it's yours alone, never committed.

## About Me
- **Name:** Your Name
- **Location:** Your City, State
- **Timezone:** America/Los_Angeles

## Family / Household
- Add family members and relevant context here

## Preferences
- Add personal preferences, routines, things to remember

## Notes
- Add anything you want your assistant to always know about you
